description: Sixth Sense DAO is an hybrid DAO that combines AMM(Automated market marker) venture & service while supporting a wide variety of projects with funding, software development, community building and Network participation. Our Team Consist of Ten Guilds, who are native in the blockchain space with experience in web 3 software development, marketing and community organisation, DEFI, UI/UX development etc. we also double as a web 3 recruitment agency through our registered company by helping  building and transitioning skilled web 2 individuals to web 3 through our internship and jobs placement programs using our already developed Dynamic job finder bot/app.
